	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/10/the-network-connection/" rel="bookmark">The Network Connection</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>With all the problems we&#8217;ve been having down here, you eventually start to become inspired to find an outlet, a way of bringing forth all your frustrations and desires into a singular vision. For some, it is art, for others it&#8217;s the urge to beat the living crap out of something.  <br />
For me, it&#8217;s music.  <br />
